{"id": 1022, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都是怎样筛选出“灵魂伴侣”的候选人？", "description": "为你那些不计其数的求爱者（如果有的话），而安排的一场初试。（题图来自：Martha Anne）", "record_count": 5544, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194522mnd1x7ca403kGyhE.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-07-08T23:11:48Z", "options": [{"id": 96512, "content": "一起旅行能开心，能一起追剧追新番，能一起看新闻，能一起聊段子", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672937}, {"id": 96513, "content": "气场", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423956}, {"id": 96514, "content": "在一起不会觉得无聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672940}, {"id": 96515, "content": "世界观、价值观、人生观相似，性格和品质不能与我相左", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 390894}, {"id": 96516, "content": "第一印象很重要！！！(๑• . •๑)", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 658796}, {"id": 96520, "content": "兴趣爱好和学历谈吐，一个喜欢红绿大布的人怎么也不会和设计师谈", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 469135}, {"id": 96335, "content": "第一感觉是否舒服", "image": null, "praise_count": 341, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671286}, {"id": 96342, "content": "看细节 交流中的细节", "image": null, "praise_count": 81, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 96358, "content": "饮食男女，人之大欲。如果这两样合拍，其他就不重要了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668847}, {"id": 96370, "content": "读书否", "image": null, "praise_count": 74, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 606440}, {"id": 96517, "content": "第一眼看的是眼缘，给机会的过程中看的是这个男的的细节、谈吐、家世背景、幽默感等等等等，只要其中一样打中心里", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 660779}, {"id": 96518, "content": "难道不应该有一双能够透视的X激光眼么", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 244661}, {"id": 96519, "content": "看感觉…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274163}, {"id": 96522, "content": "喜好相同是一方面，是否有相同吐槽的事情 感觉更关键", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 520752}, {"id": 96331, "content": "是否喜欢 新闻编辑室\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672297}, {"id": 96332, "content": "是否有趣。", "image": null, "praise_count": 301, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 638693}, {"id": 96338, "content": "听什么样的音乐 看什么样的电影 以及言行透露出来的品质", "image": null, "praise_count": 614, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672321}, {"id": 96341, "content": "能不能聊到一块儿去，没话说再好看也白搭", "image": null, "praise_count": 897, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 293164}, {"id": 96344, "content": "看他的生活。", "image": null, "praise_count": 104, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671141}, {"id": 96345, "content": "第一眼感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 552467}, {"id": 96346, "content": "脸好看+身材好+三观合+家境合+聊的来+性格互补+未来计划大体一致", "image": null, "praise_count": 92, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 425163}, {"id": 96347, "content": "首先，对方的手机里得有好奇心日报这个app。", "image": null, "praise_count": 73, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643918}, {"id": 96349, "content": "看是不是女的。（本人男）", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 189641}, {"id": 96350, "content": "是否善良，孝顺！", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672353}, {"id": 96351, "content": "笑点和三观", "image": null, "praise_count": 453, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672138}, {"id": 96352, "content": "?你们找不到那样的", "image": null, "praise_count": 150, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 603240}, {"id": 96353, "content": "ˊ_>ˋ听起来就好难啊……", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 572114}, {"id": 96354, "content": "适当时候直接挑明，以防备自己是自作多情", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 363108}, {"id": 96356, "content": "看两个人是否合适，各方面", "image": "img/option/option/20160709081734BmNwb8qyotn34IYL.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672362}, {"id": 96357, "content": "是否有共情", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 598300}, {"id": 82534, "content": "观察ta生活中是否叭唧嘴/抖腿/留指甲......", "image": null, "praise_count": 143, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 82535, "content": "考察ta喜欢汪苏泷还是后摇，看是不是有共同话题", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 96359, "content": "还是看第一眼，然后看能不能聊得来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672373}, {"id": 82536, "content": "首先还是要瞄一眼颜值，划分大段", "image": null, "praise_count": 552, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 96360, "content": "幽默好玩，却也始终如一", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595248}, {"id": 82537, "content": "看两个人的价值观是否相似", "image": null, "praise_count": 497, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 96361, "content": "在一起是否可以不伪装，真真实实做自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 107, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672376}, {"id": 82538, "content": "会先慢慢从朋友做起，从长计议", "image": null, "praise_count": 137, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 96362, "content": "能不能和我朋友相处", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 611598}, {"id": 96363, "content": "要么有趣，要么有深度", "image": null, "praise_count": 282, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672380}, {"id": 96365, "content": "相信你吹的牛逼能实现的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 52, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672389}, {"id": 96366, "content": "不能冷场", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672397}, {"id": 96367, "content": "在我画画的时候会不会安静的看书", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672398}, {"id": 96369, "content": "善良与聪明", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 658627}, {"id": 96371, "content": "问豆瓣账号", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259532}, {"id": 96372, "content": "同甘苦，共患难", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 656256}, {"id": 96373, "content": "我即使不说话，他也能让我说话让我笑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 84, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311434}, {"id": 96374, "content": "是不是真实，真诚才能打动人", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 601802}, {"id": 96376, "content": "说再多，还不是靠感觉！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 68429}, {"id": 96377, "content": "第一眼是否有反应", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664094}]}